dataset.title: eBird Reference Data Set Subsampled Demonstration Data

associatedParty.organizationName: National Center for Ecological Analysis and Synthesis (NCEAS)

abstract.para: Data used by the DataONE Exploration, Visualization, and Analysis working group for predicting spatially and temporally explicit bird migration patterns. This is a subset of the eBird Reference Data set, and has been subsetted and downsampled to provide a reasonable corpus for a technology demonstration. See the eBird Reference Dataset for the complete data.

intellectualRights.para: Attribution of data usage and distribution are expected in most circumstances, and any research papers that use the data should cite this dat apackage as a source. All data are released under CC-0 provisions (see http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/ ).
